[{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/clovaai/deep-text-recognition-benchmark/issues/comments/487453283","html_url":"https://github.com/clovaai/deep-text-recognition-benchmark/issues/6#issuecomment-487453283","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/clovaai/deep-text-recognition-benchmark/issues/6","id":487453283,"node_id":"MDEyOklzc3VlQ29tbWVudDQ4NzQ1MzI4Mw==","user":{"login":"ku21fan","id":7953971,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjc5NTM5NzE=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/7953971?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/ku21fan","html_url":"https://github.com/ku21fan","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ku21fan/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ku21fan/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ku21fan/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ku21fan/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ku21fan/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ku21fan/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ku21fan/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ku21fan/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ku21fan/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2019-04-29T05:09:41Z","updated_at":"2019-11-21T10:38:28Z","author_association":"CONTRIBUTOR","body":"Yes, some examples of SynthText dataset are weird, so we conducted some validation checks for each bounding box.\r\nWe hope that this code will help you. \r\n[crop_by_word_bb.zip](https://github.com/clovaai/deep-text-recognition-benchmark/files/3125995/crop_by_word_bb.zip)\r\n\r\n[update 2019.11.21]\r\nThe above code is used for the box label which starts with left top coordinate and ends with left bottom coordinate, \r\nsuch as `[left top x/y, right top x/y, right bottom x/y, left bottom x/y]`\r\n\r\nIf some of your box labels **_do not start with_** left top coordinate and ends with left bottom coordinate like MLT2019 datasets, \r\nsuch as `[right top x/y, right bottom x/y, left bottom x/y, left top x/y]`\r\nWe recommend using the below code, which makes simply rectangle crop images.\r\n```\r\n    x_left = min([wordBB[0][0], wordBB[0][1], wordBB[0][2], wordBB[0][3]])\r\n    x_right = max([wordBB[0][0], wordBB[0][1], wordBB[0][2], wordBB[0][3]])\r\n\r\n    y_top = min([wordBB[1][0], wordBB[1][1], wordBB[1][2], wordBB[1][3]])\r\n    y_bottom = max([wordBB[1][0], wordBB[1][1], wordBB[1][2], wordBB[1][3]])\r\n    pts1= np.float32([[x_left, y_top], [x_right, y_top], [x_right, y_bottom], [x_left, y_bottom]])\r\n\r\n    width = x_right - x_left\r\n    height = y_bottom - y_top\r\n```\r\n```\r\n            pts2 = np.float32([[0, 0],\r\n                               [width, 0],\r\n                               [width, height],\r\n                               [0, height]])\r\n```\r\n\r\ninstead of the part of the above code\r\n```\r\n            pts1 = np.float32([[wordBB[0][0], wordBB[1][0]],\r\n                               [wordBB[0][3], wordBB[1][3]],\r\n                               [wordBB[0][1], wordBB[1][1]],\r\n                               [wordBB[0][2], wordBB[1][2]]])\r\n            height = math.sqrt((wordBB[0][0] - wordBB[0][3])**2 + (wordBB[1][0] - wordBB[1][3])**2)\r\n            width = math.sqrt((wordBB[0][0] - wordBB[0][1])**2 + (wordBB[1][0] - wordBB[1][1])**2)\r\n```\r\n```\r\n            pts2 = np.float32([[0, 0],\r\n                               [0, height],\r\n                               [width, 0],\r\n                               [width, height]])\r\n```\r\n\r\nBest,","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/clovaai/deep-text-recognition-benchmark/issues/comments/487453283/reactions","total_count":7,"+1":5,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":2,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"performed_via_github_app":null,"event":"commented","actor":{"login":"ku21fan","id":7953971,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjc5NTM5NzE=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.github